        "content": "<h2>KalDB OTel Demo</h2><p>The log panels above read directly from KalDB datasets <code>otel-demo-logs</code> and <code>otel-demo-traces</code>. Expand a trace span row to copy <code>trace_id</code>, set the dashboard variable, then open the trace waterfall link.</p><p>The waterfall uses Grafana's Zipkin datasource against KalDB Query API <code>/api/v2/trace/{traceId}</code>. The trace-to-logs link searches <code>otel-demo-logs</code> for the same trace ID.</p>",
